title: Beef on Wet Pt. I with Lauren Nostro
description:
Mama mia! Here we go again! It’s a Make-A-Wish type beat this week as Jimmy and Larry dial in their old pal, the always out of pocket and newly cancer-free Lauren Nostro. Lauren joins the boys on a journey to the absolute brink as we delve and probe the deepest reaches of ourselves, including, but not limited to: how to spend your last day on earth, being a female volcel, blasting darts, copping fake Eames chairs, Buffalo’s rap scene, Breast History Month, Gianni Versace and much more on this very special, life-affirming episode of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
